    </table>
    <p>Colorado Division of Insurance data shows non-renewal complaints and premium increase complaints as the top categories from 2022 through 2025. Boulder County has the highest per-capita non-renewal complaint rate in the state, reflecting Marshall Fire aftermath. Douglas and Arapahoe counties show elevated hail-related claims dispute complaints.</p>
  </Fragment>

